src/lib/components/DashLogger.react.js.description: DashLogger component for displaying logs in real-time.

id.description: The ID used to identify this component in Dash callbacks.

loggerName.description: Name of the logger to display (for single logger view)

loggerNames.description: Names of loggers to display (for combined view)

maxLogs.description: Maximum number of logs to display

className.description: Additional class name for the logger container

style.description: Additional inline styles for the logger container

twoColumns.description: Whether to display logs in two columns (timestamp and message)

timestampFormat.description: The format string for the timestamp
